BEGIN_PGML
Is [`-3`] a solution to the equation [`2x-3=5-(4+x)\text{?}`]

>> [@DataTable(
  [
    [PGML('[`2x-3`]'),
     PGML('[`{}={}`]'),
     PGML('[`5-(4+x)`]'),
    ],
    [PGML('[_]{-9}{3}'),
     PGML('[`{}\wonder{=}{}`]'),
     PGML('[_]{4}{3}'),
    ],
  ],
      align => 'rcl',
      valign => 'middle',);@]* <<

[_]{$yesno}{5}

END_PGML

